                    "body": "<p>Use <a href=\"https://scikit-learn.org/stable/modules/generated/sklearn.preprocessing.MinMaxScaler.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">scikit-learn</a>:</p>\n<pre><code>from sklearn.preprocessing import MinMaxScaler\ndata = np.array([1,2,3]).reshape(-1, 1)\nscaler = MinMaxScaler()\nscaler.fit(data)\nprint(scaler.transform(data))\n</code></pre>\n"
